room_title: Escape room "ATEM Bomb" by Combo & Key in Portland
room_address: 10160 SW Nimbus Ave, Suite F-2 Portland, OR 97223
room_description:
Welcome to Atem Labs! We test portals and interdimensional rifts but we've gone too far and we need your help to revert the mistakes we've made!

As a side note, the creator of this escape room has...gone missing. He might be locked up in his office but we think the key might be lost in the ATEM Bomb room. You think you can help us?
